WEBVTT

00:00.613 --> 00:01.921
Do you like going to the park?

00:02.579 --> 00:03.038
Oh yeah.

00:03.409 --> 00:05.720
My friends and I play basketball there every Sunday.

00:05.993 --> 00:06.611
What about you?

00:07.477 --> 00:09.463
We ride our bikes at the park on Thursdays.

00:10.100 --> 00:12.590
Sometimes, we also go running on weekends.

00:13.230 --> 00:14.809
There's a nice path along the park.

00:15.855 --> 00:16.651
That sounds great!

00:16.987 --> 00:18.804
Is your weekend running a regular thing?

00:19.516 --> 00:21.529
No, only when the weather's good.

00:22.331 --> 00:24.994
Listen, the news says it's going to be sunny tomorrow.

00:25.877 --> 00:27.385
Would you like to run with us?

00:27.845 --> 00:28.206
Sure!

